Comment: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是中央集散中心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是郵差嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們將四處收集到的貨物暫時集中在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後領取自己負責投遞的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅露蒂 紗雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作習慣了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都知道該怎麼做了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…正在一點一點地學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有艾米前輩的指導 馬上就能學會的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是下午需要投遞的份！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠三個人分工真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒有分在同一個區了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 就來問我說像我這樣的女孩會想要什麼禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會想要鞋子呢 因為很快就會磨破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是說他把我往哪擱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 應該說他心思不夠細膩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種人就別管了唄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了 有男朋友的人就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 分完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣細分之後 配送起來也會比較輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近的船我還沒全部記住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近都是我之前所在的艦團的船 所以我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 那邊是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 過來一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 很危險的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外行人別靠近這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 麥塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪 不可以打擾別人工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你是技師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 這裡是怎麼加工的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合金的比率是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,促動器的扭矩有多大？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.69,ruby,NTP,0,310,0,,actuator
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼喜歡機械的話就來我這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近一段時間很缺人手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說皮尼歐 你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 飛機頭先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我現在想更多瞭解加爾剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧你們能找到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這艘船就以將整個船體拉起來的方針來打撈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為接收了庫蓋爾艦團的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以現在必須增加船隻的數量才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那艘船相當大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撈起來後放哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓庫羅諾亞號的農場盡快結束收割的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放那裡應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次可是大陣仗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 久等了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧 我都一身汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作後泡個澡真是爽翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你發現的沉船決定打撈上來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我的秘密武器要得到久違的出場機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 等著瞧吧 保證你嚇破膽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 在庫蓋爾艦團裡相當於是莉瑪為我帶路的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 年紀輕輕的卻很能幹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還「年紀輕輕」…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家不就只比你小一歲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 你們都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 今天雷德立大功了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過他剛才沒跟我說這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你們又一起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是恩愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加爾剛蒂亞上還真是有不少不錯的設備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 我要海藻混合飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 原大海賊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我休假中的大海賊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然自己這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且休假要暫時結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近期會有一次大型打撈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了防止被打擾 由我們負責開道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是所謂的保鏢工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你有在認真工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在接受艾米的工作指導
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快遞方面的工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所乘坐的會飛的人形機器人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說Chamber？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用於戰鬥的機械
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操縱重力在空中飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以理解語言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論在任何時刻 都會憑藉強大力量保護駕駛員的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最強的鎧甲 Machine Caliber
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的和天神的使者一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 天神…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的是Striker嗎？庫蓋爾中校所乘坐的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我來自於庫蓋爾大人的艦團
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 可以告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校和Striker到底出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現了帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼 轉移目標了？劈腿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 莉瑪的心情倒也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 如果得不到百分之百的關注 少女可是會不安的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯 艾米她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 她都悄悄去找Chamber商量了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說…雷德有沒有什麼想要的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chamber？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉所需要的食物和生活物資現在都得到了穩定的供給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指他收到了會覺得高興的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓他露出笑臉的東西…之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經判明同盟標準的娛樂程序對少尉沒有任何效果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個也不對啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎樣才能更瞭解雷德呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為 為…為什麼你們會知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是建議啦 建議…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事用不著啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾…艾米？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了怎麼了 爭風吃醋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年輕真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人莞爾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一個個都這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活充實是件好事 不過工作那邊怎麼樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打撈雖然不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你也是時候覺得擺弄機械很有趣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…等等 皮尼歐 你什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮尼歐常常會教我關於人形機器人構造方面的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可憐他天天被甲殼屁股責罵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}誰是甲殼屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都想知道中校所率領的艦團為什麼會變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在庫蓋爾大人和使者大人開始引導人們的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的船加入了他們的艦團
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦團上下將庫蓋爾大人奉為天神的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從而團結了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在利用鯨烏賊製造的叛亂結束之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗娜莉亞大人和艾蕾莉亞大人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切都發生了改變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個人都要為維持艦團獻出自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連死也不過是其中的一種手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了維持強大而捨棄弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強迫無法戰鬥的人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灌輸為集體獻身才是幸福的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這正是人類銀河同盟的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不認為中校渴望那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何人知道庫蓋爾大人到底是什麼時候死去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果中校活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果應該不會是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所認識的中校 曾經無數次拯救過我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒找到相關的資料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調查Chamber的事很不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為能從留下的操縱席上瞭解一些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它所使用的技術還是遠遠超過了舊文明的水準
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親留給妹妹麗娜莉亞的書籍已經全都在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉 沒幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些書裡有很多加爾剛蒂亞上沒有的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知這顆星球將會成為冰封的星球之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類分裂成兩大陣營開始了鬥爭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但同時也有一小群人試圖探尋其他的出路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就是那些人的後代
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個人都放下了矜持 不顧一切地想要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在鬥爭的同時啟程奔向星河世界的人們應該也是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說 那些人拋棄了地球嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是如此 我也更願意相信他們是有過一番掙扎的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開了地球的人們後來的境遇如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡只有我一個人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得 應該有些事是只有知情的我才能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在尋找是否有能與鯨烏賊交流的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否有能更加和平地 從容地共存的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這就像是我個人的贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你必須抱有這種心情才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 我一直都在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟現在也還在和希迪亞斯進行著殊死的全面戰爭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我隱約認為這是無可奈何的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…你現在不是在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前所在的宇宙在很遠的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就沒必要那樣去想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那已經和你沒有任何關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這全都是相關的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些都是人類的所為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們與鯨烏賊為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼當希迪亞斯來到地球的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的想法和同盟會是不同的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是否會已經找到了其他的道路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:21:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了活下去而必須捨棄無法替代的東西的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 不會發生那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你無論何時…就連那時…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連那個暴風雨的日子 你也和Chamber一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴風雨的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪 你都聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是有意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我說謊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 可以的話請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那場暴風雨中 雷德和Chamber怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛被沖走的船又被沖回來撞上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有進水嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.44,0:22:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經放下隔離壁了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保險起見 還是要確認一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是這個區域的最後一艘了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 開始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起重機開動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:22:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各連接部位無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:22:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 就這樣繼續警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.71,0:22:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊急聯絡！與阿爾特彌亞號之間的連接瀕臨脫落！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:18.86,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}註：阿爾特彌亞（Artemia） 俗稱豐年蝦、鹵蟲、海猴子等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.51,0:23:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.62,0:23:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報告詳情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輔助鋼索全部繃斷 連接器也損壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一部還完好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.54,0:23:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 兩舷的汽艇都無法使用？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.54,0:23:34.02,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,screw boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦團長 阿爾特彌亞號上有500多位居民
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯絡橋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然還有一架完好 但不知道能撐到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有辦法修嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙不過來 迅速修理應該是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郵件來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被害情況的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.97,0:24:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓無法控制的中型船漂流會讓整個艦團也陷入危險
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.15,0:24:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸沉阿爾特彌亞號
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.46,0:24:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾特彌亞號…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.94,0:24:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.83,0:24:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將阿爾特彌亞號全員退艦作為最優先事項
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.55,0:24:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸沉阿爾特彌亞號
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.87,0:24:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊進行引導！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.20,0:24:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗雅的船…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.36,0:24:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.41,0:24:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別慌張！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.59,0:24:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.91,0:25:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…紗雅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.46,0:25:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐還…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.68,0:25:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.21,0:25:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.25,0:25:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要炸沉的話我也一起死在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.30,0:25:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船長 別撒嬌了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.55,0:25:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我死都不會走的！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.89,0:25:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶他走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.35,0:25:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船長 我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.28,0:25:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.93,0:25:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妹妹在四處確認居民的撤離情況
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.78,0:25:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.67,0:25:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗萊斯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.13,0:25:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舵轉不動 死待在艦橋上也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.03,0:25:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.88,0:25:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這裡是艦橋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.96,0:25:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 到中央船艙為止的居民已經都撤走了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.39,0:25:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 艦橋也只剩下我一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.55,0:25:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊時間確認剩餘的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.38,0:25:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.96,0:25:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.37,0:25:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米…你怎麼來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.56,0:25:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說要棄船所以我很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.94,0:26:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在確認船上還有沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.38,0:26:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來幫忙 還剩下哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.25,0:26:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船首艙和船尾艙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.05,0:26:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去船首艙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.94,0:26:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.12,0:26:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 要放棄阿爾特彌亞號是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.16,0:26:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 現在正在組織退艦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.86,0:26:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.30,0:26:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.22,0:26:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上離開這艘船！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.39,0:26:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.45,0:26:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.54,0:26:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊時間！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.80,0:26:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.90,0:26:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.28,0:26:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.20,0:26:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.24,0:26:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.79,0:26:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.38,0:26:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等自沉處理完成後 我們也撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.09,0:26:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的只能這麼做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.17,0:27:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然要棄船…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.06,0:27:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舵不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.99,0:27:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只靠一部連接器的話 這艘船可能會撞上艦團
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.24,0:27:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在事態演變成這樣之前把船炸沉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.14,0:27:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡可是我們成長的家呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.80,0:27:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種大風暴我也從來都沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.89,0:27:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過人生在世 無能為力的事總是難免
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.27,0:27:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是阿爾特彌亞號
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.53,0:27:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨浪正在接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.02,0:27:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 快點去避難！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.13,0:27:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅露蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.12,0:27:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不太清楚 再說一遍！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.06,0:27:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.77,0:27:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.90,0:28:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.72,0:28:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.28,0:28:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.59,0:28:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.84,0:28:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.27,0:28:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,檢測到船舶的過度傾斜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.51,0:28:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chamber！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.28,0:28:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 紗雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.65,0:28:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.34,0:28:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.49,0:29:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.90,0:29:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經突破極限傾斜角度！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.35,0:29:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chamber 最大功率！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.79,0:29:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.72,0:29:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 鋼索呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.25,0:29:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在撐著 能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.81,0:29:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 拉起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.71,0:29:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.73,0:29:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好！加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.85,0:29:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這可糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.66,0:29:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.74,0:29:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.51,0:30:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接收到緊急通信
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.30,0:30:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聽我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.93,0:30:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾特彌亞號被沖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.02,0:30:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗雅和艾米還在上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.52,0:30:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.63,0:30:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該船舶的運行控制已失效 推測已經無法掌舵
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.38,0:30:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在漂流嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.03,0:30:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.94,0:30:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.23,0:30:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在又不能離開這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.27,0:30:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 要撐住啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.81,0:30:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.40,0:30:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 破廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.38,0:30:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回裡面去！穿上這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.54,0:30:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.62,0:30:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟 糟了 船正在往回飄
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.91,0:31:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船體開始恢復平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.78,0:31:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了 船體開始恢復直立了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.64,0:31:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傾斜角度逐漸減小
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.81,0:31:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推測正在轉入安定狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.32,0:31:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.88,0:32:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.66,0:32:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威脅級別 下調
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.87,0:32:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來發生過這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.31,0:32:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時是因為有Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.77,0:32:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那傢伙已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.54,0:32:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算現在發生了同樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.83,0:32:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德也肯定不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.70,0:32:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為總是為自己所能做到的事竭盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.63,0:32:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你的為人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.47,0:33:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 開始下沉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.74,0:33:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝羅茲 捕撈框正常下降
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.70,0:33:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 大家都聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.08,0:33:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來要讓一艘船從墓場中復生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.95,0:33:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是寶貝中的寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.05,0:33:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好把它撈上來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.02,0:33:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.00,0:33:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認周邊的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.24,0:34:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮尼歐 有你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.11,0:34:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.93,0:34:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？你不用接著去送貨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.77,0:34:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的工作到此就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.29,0:34:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心雷德嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.62,0:34:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.33,0:34:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ok 就這樣保持警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.23,0:34:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮尼歐 放出固定錨
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.26,0:34:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好咧！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.38,0:34:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 你們幾個準備好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.50,0:34:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.68,0:34:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一班 將引導鋼索連接到船體上
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.30,0:35:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二班 將主鋼索從船底繞過
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.12,0:35:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認連接情況！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.05,0:35:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認完畢！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.69,0:35:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進入最後工序了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.98,0:35:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.38,0:35:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.45,0:35:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.49,0:35:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼索好像被什麼給勾住了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.89,0:35:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.97,0:35:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要崩塌了！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.17,0:35:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊點 趕快！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.93,0:36:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 有我撐著！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.37,0:36:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.91,0:36:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.88,0:36:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德還在下面！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.10,0:36:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.87,0:36:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切斷鋼索的連接！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.54,0:36:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.87,0:36:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.53,0:37:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氧氣存量！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.90,0:37:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.49,0:37:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,備用氧氣罐打開
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.17,0:37:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二氧化碳吸收劑緊急投入
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.82,0:37:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電池存量已確認
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.82,0:37:35.23,ruby,NTP,0,230,0,,battery
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.41,0:37:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制器正常
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.41,0:37:37.24,ruby,NTP,0,110,0,,Manipulator
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.56,0:37:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認通信狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.51,0:37:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.33,0:37:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說通信纜線…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.68,0:37:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 誰來回句話！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.29,0:37:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.30,0:37:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.70,0:38:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面到底發生了什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.10,0:38:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.51,0:38:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然有瓦斯湧出來 周邊崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.00,0:38:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德那小子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.23,0:38:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算還活著 備用氧氣也該用盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.43,0:38:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…那就快點潛回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.35,0:38:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在接近那裡太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.92,0:38:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救助隊也會被捲入進去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.38,0:38:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.81,0:38:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.38,0:38:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能想想辦法嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.96,0:38:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝羅茲…！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.57,0:38:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝羅茲！我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.15,0:38:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有應答
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.79,0:39:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是Machine Caliber K6821駕駛員 雷德少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.35,0:39:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.44,0:39:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有應答
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.71,0:39:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推測由於希迪亞斯的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.35,0:39:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,導致整個機庫處於漂流狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.63,0:39:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊給我恢復通信 你這廢物！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.94,0:39:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建議關閉電波發射機能
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.67,0:39:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.00,0:39:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認到多數希迪亞斯的生體反應
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.96,0:39:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本機有被探知的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.24,0:39:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.09,0:39:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能等著被牠們吞噬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.72,0:39:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快發出求救信號！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.72,0:39:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能相信你這種機器的判斷！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.91,0:39:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.29,0:39:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有判斷都由專屬駕駛員雷德少尉進行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.56,0:39:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴官能力的充分發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.73,0:39:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可使本機導出打開局面的最佳方法
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.85,0:40:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說你的威力取決於我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.13,0:40:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定 期待貴官做出明智的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.59,0:40:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.98,0:40:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能死在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.62,0:40:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是你還是我 都一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.73,0:40:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.49,0:40:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是駕駛員支援啟發連接系統
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.42,0:40:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓貴官獲得更多的成果便是我的存在意義所在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.64,0:40:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.93,0:40:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時 他讓我要相信自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.42,0:40:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且他說他相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.54,0:40:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西也撐不了太久
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.07,0:40:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想 快想想！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.89,0:41:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多來點 把在這的傢伙都拉過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.01,0:41:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儲氣瓶不夠 能搬多少來就搬多少來
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.01,0:41:52.49,ruby,NTP,0,540,0,,Bombe
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.50,0:41:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得這樣才行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.78,0:42:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集各位船主
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.55,0:42:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向他們請求人力和物資協助
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.27,0:42:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 安排醫療隊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.70,0:42:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.26,0:42:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.67,0:42:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去救他！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.87,0:42:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.62,0:42:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.72,0:42:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.31,0:42:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.35,0:42:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.27,0:42:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.72,0:42:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也應該能幫上什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.30,0:42:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.64,0:42:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該做的是另一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.81,0:42:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.88,0:42:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用笑臉去迎接這些不要命的傻瓜們和雷德的歸來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.38,0:42:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會平安帶他回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.18,0:42:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.22,0:43:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼說定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.79,0:43:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.18,0:43:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒找到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.23,0:43:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凱奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.71,0:43:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你們慢吞吞的搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.75,0:43:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.48,0:44:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有我在附近了還在這種地方搞出死人來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.75,0:44:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是存心想讓我睡不好覺麼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.09,0:44:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凱奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.04,0:44:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪塊地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.82,0:44:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這縫隙裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.42,0:44:20.33,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,Amigo
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.42,0:44:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夥計
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.79,0:44:22.34,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,Storonzo
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.79,0:44:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.34,0:44:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.62,0:44:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好拉凱奇 就這麼撐住
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.42,0:44:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.47,0:44:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還活著！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.87,0:44:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.47,0:45:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把浮筒用的壓縮空氣釋放到駕駛艙裡了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.51,0:45:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.34,0:45:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.43,0:45:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會互相配合 同時把這裡撐開
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.32,0:45:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就在這個瞬間把四肢和浮筒從軀幹部分離
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.88,0:45:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.73,0:45:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信同伴！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.55,0:45:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.43,0:45:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒數3下就開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.55,0:45:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.65,0:45:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.86,0:45:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.11,0:45:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.87,0:45:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在 雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.58,0:45:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.04,0:46:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機體從裡面出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.14,0:46:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德平安無事！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.88,0:46:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.26,0:46:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.69,0:46:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.31,0:46:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.00,0:46:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.71,0:47:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.36,0:47:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.61,0:47:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.18,0:47:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.06,0:49:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 進入下一個階段
Comment: 0,0:49:22.70,0:49:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解【這句其實我聽不懂…………我覺得應該是外星語吧Orz
