Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:52.61,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}將聚散離合深埋心間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:59.49,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏出前進的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:06.63,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}記憶總以柔和的觸感
