Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:15.25,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}天空的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:18.41,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}與濤聲一同作響
