Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:49.84,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}無論面對怎樣的風向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:54.02,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始終朝著自由的所在
